# Dropbox sync (Phase 3, optional). Leave empty to hide the feature entirely.
#
# Setup:
# 1. https://www.dropbox.com/developers/apps -> Create app
# 2. "Scoped access" -> "App folder" (NOT "Full Dropbox" — this limits a
#    leaked token to just this app's own folder, never the rest of the
#    account)
# 3. Permissions tab: enable files.content.write, files.content.read
# 4. Settings tab: add this exact Redirect URI (dev and prod, one per line)
#      http://localhost:5173/
#      http://localhost:4173/
#      https://<your-site>.netlify.app/
# 5. Copy the "App key" (NOT the app secret — this is a public PKCE client
#    and must never use the secret) into PUBLIC_DROPBOX_CLIENT_ID below,
#    and also set it as an env var in the Netlify site settings.
PUBLIC_DROPBOX_CLIENT_ID=
